videos.description: M. Farrell made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Notre Dame using 3-point shooting to counter Florida State's height

videos.description: Notre Dame's Bonzie Colson gets the ball off the great bounce pass from Matt Farrell, makes the layup and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Colson gets the hoop and the harm

videos.description: Former Notre Dame head coach and ESPN analyst Digger Phelps is in attendance as Notre Dame and Florida State face off
videos.headline: Digger Phelps in attendance as Notre Dame looks to upset Florida State

videos.description: Notre Dame head coach Mike Brey talks about his team's 1st half strategy that gives them a 40-31 lead at the half.
videos.headline: Notre Dame head coach Mike Brey talks about his team's 1st half strategy that gives them a 40-31 lead at the half

videos.description: Notre Dame's Rex Pfluger fouls Florida State's Xavier Rathan-Mayes and Michael Ojo shoves Pfluger in the second half.
videos.headline: Things get chippy between ND and FSU

videos.description: Bonzie Colson gets his 1000th career point on a great tip in off a missed 3-point shot.
videos.headline: Bonzie Colson reaches 1,000 career points on beautiful tip in play

videos.description: Florida State's Dwayne Bacon misses the 3-pointer and Terance Mann follows through with the dunk.
videos.headline: Mann comes through with putback dunk

videos.description: Notre Dame's Bonzie Colson throws down a two-handed jam to help pad the lead for the Fighting Irish.
videos.headline: Colson slams down dunk
Vasturia dunk puts a cap on Notre Dame upset win over Florida State

videos.description: Postgame interview with Notre Dame head coach Mike Brey on the team's defensive performance and the play of Bonzie Colson in Notre Dame's 84-72 win over Florida State.
